description: This newly constructed 3 bedroom, plus office, 2.5 bathroom duplex home offers 2,257 square feet of living space, and parking! As you step into the breathtaking bilevel home, you are welcomed by dramatic 20-foot cathedral ceilings. The chefs kitchen boasts glossy white cabinetry, zodiac ashen gray quartz countertops and backsplash, stainless steel appliances and elegant under counter lighting. The spacious primary suite offers plenty of space for a king bed and enjoys a large walk-in closet as well as an en-suite bath with a dual vanity, radiant flooring and designer tile! This remarkable home fulfills all the requirements of its fortunate new owners with central heat/ac, in-unit washer/dryer, smart thermostats and controlled building access. Located steps from Thomas Park, near the intersection of East and West Broadway, this home is walking distance to miles of shoreline, public transportation and South Boston's best restaurants, bars, shopping!
